  <h2>Architecture Overview</h2>

  <p>
    LeadEcho is composed of three independently deployable services that work together to monitor social platforms,
    score intent signals, and surface high-value leads in a unified inbox.
  </p>

  <pre><code>┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     LeadEcho Stack                       │
├──────────────────┬──────────────────┬───────────────────┤
│  Go Backend      │  React Dashboard │  Chrome Extension │
│  (Chi + pgx)     │  (TanStack)      │  (WXT + MV3)      │
│  port 8090       │  port 3100       │                   │
├──────────────────┴──────────────────┴───────────────────┤
│  PostgreSQL (pgvector)  │  Redis (queue/cache)           │
├─────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────┤
│  Sidecars: Pinchtab · Camoufox · Scrapling               │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘</code></pre>

  <h2>Tech Stack</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Layer</th>
        <th>Technology</th>
        <th>Purpose</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Backend language</td>
        <td><code>Go 1.25+</code></td>
        <td>API server, background monitor, scoring pipeline</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>HTTP router</td>
        <td><code>Chi</code></td>
        <td>Lightweight, idiomatic routing + middleware</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Database driver</td>
        <td><code>pgx/v5</code></td>
        <td>High-performance PostgreSQL driver</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Query codegen</td>
        <td><code>sqlc</code></td>
        <td>Type-safe SQL → Go structs, no ORM</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Vector search</td>
        <td><code>pgvector</code></td>
        <td>1024-dim HNSW cosine similarity for semantic matching</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Logging</td>
        <td><code>zerolog</code></td>
        <td>Zero-alloc structured JSON logs</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Frontend</td>
        <td><code>React + Vite</code></td>
        <td>Dashboard SPA</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Router</td>
        <td><code>TanStack Router</code></td>
        <td>Type-safe file-based routing</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Data fetching</td>
        <td><code>TanStack Query</code></td>
        <td>Server state, caching, background refetch</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Extension framework</td>
        <td><code>WXT 0.19</code></td>
        <td>MV3 Chrome extension build tooling</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>AI embeddings</td>
        <td><code>Voyage AI</code></td>
        <td>voyage-3-lite 1024-dim semantic vectors</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>LLM scoring</td>
        <td><code>GLM / OpenAI</code></td>
        <td>Intent classification, reply drafting</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

